  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"3 left parenthesis k x plus 13 right parenthesis equals StartFraction 48 Over 17 EndFraction x plus 36\"><mn>3</mn><mo>(</mo><mi>k</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>13</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac>\n\t<mn>48</mn>\n\t<mn>17</mn>\n</mfrac>\n<mrow>\n\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mn>36</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In the given equation, <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math> is a constant. The equation has no solution. What is the value of <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
